notes: Although last in on Labor’s ticket, Lisa SINGH was elected rather than Catryana BILYK and John SHORT because she received a considerable number of below the line preferences that ranked her above these two candidates. This is a good example of the advatages of voting below the line.
Although elected in 2016, Stephen PARRY was disqualified due to foreign citizenship. He was replaced by Richard COLLBECK.
Although elected in 2016, David BUSHBY resigned in order to be nominated as Australia's consul-general in Chicago. He was replaced by Wendy ASKEW.
Although not elected in 2016, Richard COLLBECK replaced Stephen PARRY, who was disqualified due to foreign citizenship.
Although elected in 2016, Jacqui LAMBIE was disqualified due to citizenship. She was replaced by Steve MARTIN, who is now in the Nationals.
